                    from the Dutch Govt. However, prior to that date the nomenclature was changed
                    from West Indies to Netherlands West Indies and vice versa on several occasions
                    and in each instance the commission was made out in accordance with the way in
                    which it was carried in the Foreign Service List.</p>
